{"tid":949251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國起訴兩名中國黑客","createTime":"2018-12-20T16:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T20:16:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fad374ec32652c5461cb5cb2cb4d57ba7ed9647","tid":949251,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國起訴兩名中國黑客，指他們非法進入多個美國政府部門及私人公司的網絡，盜取機密資料。<br />\n<br />\n美國副司法部長羅森斯坦在華盛頓宣布有關決定，同時公布的起訴書，指譯音姓朱及姓張的被告隸屬一個叫APT10的組織並與中國國安部合作，美國指兩名被告入侵為多間國際大企業、提供雲端運算及資料儲存的科技公司，藉此進入至少45家科技公司及政府部門的電腦竊取機密資訊，又盜取十萬名美國海軍士兵的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n美國指控中國違反兩國在2015年達成避免偷竊公司知識產權的網絡攻擊行為協議。美國傳媒分析指，在中美貿易戰背景下，美國就起訴中國黑客將令兩國的貿易談判增添不明朗因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=331483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331483&d=yFU820QwUkAd0YsRAN6Rav7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4c8de99e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331483&h=62cb37eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=331483</a>"},{"pid":"d957f9e0dcfb94080a85ec3291fbf99857249617","tid":949251,"uid":41888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"侵侵好波 繼續郁支国<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcc699a66d7e2e965bd6fd28fe7c9534ff7a395","tid":949251,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"所以邊個國家用華為死緊"},{"pid":"bde7f2e568871047b9797ca10e7e934b5b7f7c99","tid":949251,"uid":106810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"其實有咩用，條友唔去美國咪得<br />\n<br />\n仲要無得防"},{"pid":"8798810ac23b62a272dcd4dd410826af0c12620c","tid":949251,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bde7f2e568871047b9797ca10e7e934b5b7f7c99","tid":949251,"uid":106810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":